<paragraph id="C67A7388C9C5C368A5EDB916748A7F95" pageId="121" pageNumber="122">Male holotype (AP415) from California, Inyo County, Deep Springs Valley sand dunes, 37.3333, -118.0167 4, 1536m, coll. D. Giuliani 19.xii.1973; male paratype (AP424) from California, Mono County, 14.5km, N of Bishop, 37.4939, -118.3977 4, 1300m, coll. D. Giuliani 29.vii.1980. Deposited in CAS.</paragraph>
